Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很完美
